title: Triathlon types
tags:
- triathlon
---


1. Spring

  Swim - 750m
  Bike - 20km
  Run - 5km


2. Olympic

  Swim - 1500m
  Bike - 40km
  Run - 10km


3. Half ironman - 70.3

  Swim - 1.2 miles (1.93km)
  Bike - 56 miles (90.12km)
  Run - 13.1 miles (21.08km)


4. Ironman - 140.6

  Swim - 2.4 miles (3.86km)
  Bike - 112 miles (180.24km)
  Run - 26.2 miles (42.16km)
